  <brief_title>Study on the Ability of Virtual Reality Glasses in Anxiety and Pain Reduction in 50 Women Undergoing Amniocentesis or Feticide</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Ability of Virtual Reality in Anxiety and Pain Reduction in Women Undergoing Amniocentesis or Feticide</official_title>
