  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Both amniocenteses and especially feticide are procedures that incorporate both anxiety and&#xD;
      pain. As anxiety and pain can be reduced when using a distraction, The investigators&#xD;
      speculate that the use of virtual reality glasses during these procedures will elevate both&#xD;
      anxiety and pain.&#xD;
&#xD;
      The investigators will examine this hypothesis by comparing two groups of participants who&#xD;
      undergo amniocentesis or feticide, one group will undergo the procedure while using virtual&#xD;
      reality glasses and the other without the use of the glasses.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
